d-hosts-file error messages to say `JmDNS test` instead of `JmDNS 0.2 test`.\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0693a828dfdeee53016a11040e1a9c81a1952fa5adce3a8f42\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 606, "output": 901, "cacheRead": 79872, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 81379, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779500032976, "responseId": "resp_0693a828dfdeee53016a110401c05081a1944ae2ff147fde26"}}
